@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api

### Giorno corrente
GET {{baseUrl}}/day

### Avanza il giorno
POST {{baseUrl}}/advance-day

### Reset completo del sistema
POST {{baseUrl}}/reset

### Lista banchine
GET {{baseUrl}}/berths

### Lista navi
GET {{baseUrl}}/ships

### Lista navi filtrate per stato
GET {{baseUrl}}/ships?status=Pending

### Registra una nuova nave
POST {{baseUrl}}/ships
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "MSC Test",
  "size": "M",
  "arrivalDay": 1,
  "occupationDuration": 5,
  "status": "Pending"
}

### Lista assegnazioni
GET {{baseUrl}}/assignments

### Crea assegnazione
POST {{baseUrl}}/assignments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "shipId": 1,
  "berthId": 3
}

### Storico PortLog
GET {{baseUrl}}/portlogs